description: Face-to-face aged care support is now available at dedicated Services Australia service centres,You can book an appointment to speak to an Aged Care Specialist Officer (ACSO) in person by calling 1800 227 475 on weekdays from 8am to 5pm.The face-to-face support will rollout to 80 locations by December 2022.
